{"tid":311060,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"1874算唔算毒撚悲歌","createTime":"2017-07-06T09:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T10:53:45.000Z","uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca447d8f476d1279243ea4e2a842b3fa236edd39","tid":311060,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"先不計因電影而另有解法的歌詞意思<br />\n淨係聽歌<br />\n似講緊一個毒撚成世都識唔到女<br />\n就開始ff話命中註定個人係第個年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣呃自己，最後都係孤獨寂寞<br />\n首歌不斷幻想同佢生活係點，就算係戰地都會好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實幻想得愈多愈sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到我好傷心，就好似講緊我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"4d9b37f49f2e5114086666561f47af9ee50b9285","tid":311060,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"從來沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fca2134b5654a97b948f7c9c7aef57b84ecc69f","tid":311060,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254fff989e8b52969c05cb3af3e7637f0af54b3d","tid":311060,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:10:21.000Z","msg":"套電影都正<br />\n陳醫生做"},{"pid":"3d209f86bcd5928bd23a3fbc9c537f4ba3f3d5c5","tid":311060,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"無人聽1874<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b70369a6a53c514bb32d076e218f32d52d20ee","tid":311060,"uid":45505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>從來沒有<img src=\"/assets/fa